title: This seems to be a popular font with many online marketers.
author: TheJedi

comments.content: If the type is live on the site (you can select individual characters or words with your cursor), please provide the URL—the font information can be read from the CSS file.
Unfortunately, it is not live. Whoever designed it converted it to an image. I'm assuming it's not a common font that all browsers could handle. Thanks for the suggestion, though.
I believe we have a winner! Thank you both for your help.
